channel.title: [tut] runescape interfaces
channel.description:
in your extracted cache find the interfaces folder
in that you should see lots of .int files.
.int means delphi interface unit.
for more information on that visit this website
http://filext.com/detaillist.php?extdetail=INT
now to download the program that opens and loads and etc. etc.
there is no specific link i have because a friend sent it to me but ill upload it and everything but if youd like to find the link
go to
www.borland.com
then in the search bar search for
delphi interface unit
this wasnt really a very good tut on viewing them more just information on how they were made and what programs they used.
i hope somebody found this useful
- bomb
